bus A320neo - PR-YRH - Azul Linhas A\u00e9reas - During the party ceremony - Azul 10 years\" data-id=\"1138872004\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1138872004/image_1138872004.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1138872004/image_1138872004.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1138872004/image_1138872004.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1138872004/image_1138872004.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1138872004/image_1138872004.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1138872004/image_1138872004.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1138872004/image_1138872004.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1138872004/image_1138872004.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Herbert Pictures</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>A year ago, I <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4652433-azul-stock-still-a-strong-buy-but-watch-oil-prices-and-macroeconomics\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4652433-azul-stock-still-a-strong-buy-but-watch-oil-prices-and-macroeconomics\" target=\"_blank\">covered</a> <strong>Azul</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AZUL\" title=\"Azul S.A.\">AZUL</a></span>) just as the stock had done more than well with a 42.1% return compared to a 6.4% downward price development for the U.S. Global Jets ETF (<a href=\"https: